demo.name: AI Safety Fellowship - Policy Track Application
demo.description:
The AI Safety Fellowship's Policy Track offers a weekly reading group focusing on AI Policy with discussions and debates. Participants and alumni are preferred candidates for a research program with mentorship and funding. The application is due by September 5th, 11:59 PM EST, and the fellowship is expected to start on September 15th.
